Republic of Korea; Vuk Jeremi&#263;, Minister for Foreign Affairs of Serbia;  
</p>
<p> (d) At the 4th meeting, on the same day: Huda Alban, Minister for Human 
Rights of Yemen; Ndelu Seretse, Minister for Defence, Justice and Security of Botswana; 
