Thailand, Uzbekistan. 
</p>
<p>20. At the same meeting, the panellist Mohammed Naciri made his concluding remarks. 
</p>
<p><b> D. General segment 
</b></p>
<p>21. At the 6th meeting, on 3 March 2010, a general segment was held, during which the 
following addressed the Council: 
</p>
<p> (a) Representatives of States Members of the Council: Chile, China, Egypt, 
France, Hungary, India, Indonesia, Italy, Mexico, Pakistan, Qatar, Russian Federation, 
Ukraine, Uruguay; 
</p>
