<p><b>  Human rights and arbitrary deprivation of nationality 
</b></p>
<p>145. At the 41st meeting, on 24 March 2010, the representative of the Russian Federation 
introduced draft resolution A/HRC/13/L.4, sponsored by Belarus and the Russian 
Federation and co-sponsored by Bolivia (Plurinational State of), Cuba and Peru. 
Subsequently, Kazakhstan, Kyrgyzstan, Nicaragua and Serbia joined the co-sponsors.  
</p>
<p>146. At the same meeting, the representative of the Russian Federation orally revised the 
draft resolution by modifying the fourth and twelfth preambular paragraphs, adding a new 
fourteenth preambular paragraph and modifying paragraphs 4, 7, 10, 13 and 15. 
</p>
<p>147. Also at the same meeting, the draft resolution, as orally revised, was adopted 
without a vote. 
</p>
<p>148. For the text as adopted, see part one, chapter I, resolution 13/2. 
</p>
