Ukraine, United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland, Uruguay, 
Zambia; 
</p>
<p><i>Against</i>: 
United States of America. 
</p>
<p>802. For the text as adopted, see part one, chapter I, resolution 13/6. 
</p>
<p><b>  Israeli settlements in the Occupied Palestinian Territory, including East Jerusalem, 
and in the occupied Syrian Golan 
</b></p>
